OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMining giant says it       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Funderpaid workers for 13   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fyears                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Australian mining giant BHP says it    
OL,6, underpaid current and former workers   
OL,7, across the country for 13 years.       
OL,9,FAround 28,500 employees received less  
OL,10,Fholiday than they were entitled to, a  
OL,11,Freview conducted by the firm found.    
OL,13,FMeanwhile, 400 workers did not get     
OL,14,Fadditional allowances "due to an error 
OL,15,Fwith the employment entity."           
OL,17,FBHP says it has reported the incident  
OL,18,Fto the authorities and the errors will 
OL,19,Fcost the company up to $280m (#225m)   
OL,20,Fbefore taxes.                          
